This spell casts a random wizard spell on the target creature, which could be a spell of any level between 5 and 8. The nature of the spell depends on the target. If the target is an enemy, they will receive a harmful spell, but if the target is an ally, they will receive a beneficial spell. Targeting restrictions are obeyed (a spell that can only target the caster will not be rolled unless the target is the caster).

