@12927    = ~Ring of Pain Amplification~
@12928    = ~This cursed ring fuses itself to the wearer's finger, only coming off if a spell is used to remove the curse. While it is in use, the wearer suffers extra damage from all attacks. Often given to the victims of horrific torture, the ring also regenerates the wearer, allowing them to suffer even more pain without dying. Lovitarians are known to create these items and distribute them throughout the realms for their own amusement.

STATISTICS:

Vulnerability: -5 Slashing Resistance
Vulnerability: -5 Piercing Resistance
Vulnerability: -5 Crushing Resistance
Regeneration: User regenerates 1 hit point per second
Special: Can only be removed by a Remove Curse spell~
